      "index": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was unexpected Commander {COMMANDER.FirstName}.\n\nAs I was just explaining to your Captain and Mr. Madeira, I have a bottle of 3020 Chianti somewhere in the <i>Jade Dream</i> perfect for the occasion... can't think why we shouldn't open it while we can. \n\n",
