    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c7d86fdaa94db6bdc326c93"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Bob and I disagreed about the current priority but we decided that you should take the call, Commander. \n\nIt's either taking down the ISF first and then reaching the ComStar compound to deliver an HPG message to Luthien. Or we can travel to the facility first to send the message and then deal with the ISF. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "<color=#85DBF6FF>[Story Decision: Escort Chandrasekhar to send HPG message.]</color> Let us try to reach the ComStar facility first. It's better to gain time than to engage the ISF.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 10,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c793ab817749b8876df106f"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        },
        {
          "responseText": "<color=#85DBF6FF>[Story Decision: Pre-emptive strike the ISF.]</color> We need to solve this situation now, while we're still strong. The ISF will not be expecting us to move against them.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
